            </titleStmt>
            <publicationStmt>
                <p>Unpublished edition in progress.</p>
            </publicationStmt>
            <sourceDesc>
                <p>A new, born-digital diplomatic edition of the U4 manuscript of the Iliad,
                    Marcianus Graecus Z.458. Diplomatic edition based on a digital facsimile
                    prepared by the Center for Hellenic Studies in collaboration with the Biblioteca
                    Marciana, M. Zorzi, Director.</p>
                <p>The "template" text is based on the Venetus B manuscript, and is being corrected
                    to a true diplomatic edition of the U4 manuscription.</p>
            </sourceDesc>
        </fileDesc>
        <profileDesc>
            <langUsage>
                <language ident="grc">Greek, in pre-composed UTF-8</language>
                <language ident="eng">English</language>
            </langUsage>
        </profileDesc>
